divs: Sighting Detailsi had just got on the express-way heading east on I-20 east heading towards greensboro. the sky was clear the stars were bright i noticed what i thought was a larger than normal star but the more i looked at it i realized it was closer to earth than the other stars and really large. as i was watching it i noticed it hadnt moved when all of a sudden it just took off. i knew it wasnt a plane or any aircraft we have there was no red rocket fuel streak of anything. it was gone in secs i knew nothing we have could have moved that fast. it went from not moving to being gone out of my site in seconds. i dont know what i seen i just know it was something unusal and i will always wonder.
